com.dlsc.flexgantt.command.layer

Class DefaultDeleteMultipleTimelineObjectsCommand

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.dlsc.flexgantt.command.AbstractCommand

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ICommand, Serializable

    public class DefaultDeleteMultipleTimelineObjectsCommand
extends AbstractCompoundCommand<DefaultDeleteTimelineObjectCommand>
    A command that deletes several timeline objects at the same time from a Gantt chart model. This command will only work in situations where the model is an instance of DefaultGanttChartModel, the timeline object implements the ITimelineObject interface, and the tree node implements the IGanttChartNode interface.
